OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775120518
OL,3,CITV News unveils rare footage of
OL,4,CPrincess Diana's iconic 1997 Angola
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FThe clip is part of a new episode of
OL,8,FReporting History, in which Steve
OL,9,FScott - ITV News' Africa Correspondent
OL,10,Fat the time - accompanied the princess
OL,11,Fon a visit to the country as part of
OL,12,Fher campaign against landmines.
OL,14,FDiana's visit came at the height of
OL,15,Finternational debate over landmine use
OL,16,Fand drew criticism from sections of
OL,17,Fthe tabloid press and the then-
OL,18,FConservative government, which
OL,19,Fsuggested her stance aligned with Tony
OL,20,FBlair's Labour Party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775120518
OL,3,CITV News unveils rare footage of
OL,4,CPrincess Diana's iconic 1997 Angola
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FThe newly-aired archive footage shows
OL,8,FDiana directly addressing the
OL,9,Fcontroversy in a sit-down with
OL,10,Freporters.
OL,12,FScott suggests: "Can we ask the
OL,13,Fquestion about the political role?"
OL,15,FDiana responds: "I'd have thought that
OL,16,Fwas the most important question out of
OL,17,Fthe two. I'd go for that one."
OL,19,FScott asks if she means the political
OL,20,Fquestion, and Diana nods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775120518
OL,3,CITV News unveils rare footage of
OL,4,CPrincess Diana's iconic 1997 Angola
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FDiana's team seems reluctant, with
OL,8,Fsomeone off-camera saying: "No, not
OL,9,Fthe political one, you don't mean the
OL,10,Fpolitical one."
OL,12,FBut she pushes back, insisting Scott's
OL,13,Fquestion is the one she would like to
OL,14,Fanswer.
OL,16,FDuring her time in Angola, Diana
OL,17,Ffamously walked through a minefield
OL,18,Fcleared by the Halo Trust to highlight
OL,19,Fthe plight of those maimed by military
OL,20,Fmunitions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
