PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775120518
OL,3,CITV News unveils rare footage of
OL,4,CPrincess Diana's iconic 1997 Angola
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FThe famous images of the princess made
OL,8,Fglobal headlines and prompted the
OL,9,Fsigning of a landmine ban in Ottawa in
OL,10,F1998, a year after her death.
OL,12,FIn the interview, Diana goes on to say
OL,13,Fthe political storm over her campaign
OL,14,Fwas "merely a distraction, because I
OL,15,Fam not a political figure, I am a
OL,16,Fhumanitarian figure and always have
OL,17,Fbeen and always will be."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775120518
OL,3,CITV News unveils rare footage of
OL,4,CPrincess Diana's iconic 1997 Angola
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FScott told Reporting History presenter
OL,8,FTom Bradby that he ended up getting on
OL,9,Fthe same flight as Diana, where he
OL,10,Fspoke to her about being a mother and
OL,11,Fher plans for her two sons, Prince
OL,12,FWilliam and Prince Harry.
OL,14,FHe recalled: "Despite the fact that
OL,15,Fthis campaign was very important to
OL,16,Fher now and she was going to continue
OL,17,Fworking on it, she said her priority
OL,18,Fwas her boys and would continue to be
OL,19,Fher boys, and that's where she would
OL,20,Fbe focusing most of her energy going
OL,21,Fforward."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775120518
OL,3,CITV News unveils rare footage of
OL,4,CPrincess Diana's iconic 1997 Angola
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FReflecting on her death just seven
OL,8,Fmonths later, Scott said: "The woman
OL,9,Fthat I spoke to about her sons and how
OL,10,Fimportant they were to her, suddenly
OL,11,Fthose boys did not have that mother".
OL,13,FYou can find out more in the latest
OL,14,Fepisode of Reporting History,
OL,15,Favailable on ITVX, YouTube, and all
OL,16,Fmajor podcast platforms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
